---
description: Code conventions for the study-desk app
globs: ["study-desk/src/**/*.{ts,tsx,css}"]
---

- Functional components only, no class components
- No `any` types — use strict TypeScript
- Plain CSS with custom properties — no CSS-in-JS, no Tailwind, no CSS modules
- Prop drilling with useCallback/useMemo — no React Context at this scale
- Mobile breakpoint at 980px in App.css
- Run `npx eslint src/` and `npx tsc -b --noEmit` before committing
- User runs Windows + PowerShell — use temp files for multi-line git commits (no heredoc)
